OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781432282
OL,3,CJudge highlights 'irony' of social
OL,4,Cmedia videos helping to catch
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FA judge has spoken of the "irony" of
OL,8,Fviolent protesters being caught thanks
OL,9,Fto videos shared on social media by
OL,10,Fparticipants in the disorder in
OL,11,FSouthampton.
OL,13,FThe comments by Judge William Mousley
OL,14,FKC came as he handed out prison terms
OL,15,Fto three more offenders ` bringing the
OL,16,Ftotal so far to 13.
OL,26,@oD@[OUoD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/14
