CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781432282
OL,3,CJudge highlights 'irony' of social
OL,4,Cmedia videos helping to catch
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FDuring the sentencing hearing,
OL,8,FSouthampton Crown Court was shown
OL,9,Fvideo footage of the disorder,
OL,10,Fincluding clips posted on social media
OL,11,Fby some of the protesters, as well as
OL,12,Fpolice body-worn video and aerial
OL,13,Fdrone footage.
OL,15,FJudge Mousley said: "It's something of
OL,16,Fan irony that so many of these
OL,17,Foffenders have been caught and
OL,18,Fprosecuted because people in the crowd
OL,19,Fwere filming what was going on, which
OL,20,Fthey may not have envisaged at the
OL,21,Ftime."
OL,26,@wD@UOU}D@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
