OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781432282
OL,3,CJudge highlights 'irony' of social
OL,4,Cmedia videos helping to catch
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FA 36-year-old man has also pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to violent disorder by
OL,9,F"launching" a frying pan at officers.
OL,11,FRyan Atkinson, 36, of Highcliff
OL,12,FAvenue, Southampton, who is the 22nd
OL,13,Fperson to be charged after the protest
OL,14,Fon June 2, entered his plea at
OL,15,FSouthampton Magistrates' Court.
OL,17,FHe was remanded in custody to be
OL,18,Fsentenced at the crown court on June
OL,19,F29.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/14
