OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781432282
OL,3,CJudge highlights 'irony' of social
OL,4,Cmedia videos helping to catch
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FAt the crown court, three men were
OL,8,Fjailed for violent disorder during the
OL,9,Funrest, which followed the murder of
OL,10,Fstudent Henry Nowak.
OL,12,FHarry Varney, 34, of Southampton, was
OL,13,Fsentenced to three years imprisonment;
OL,14,FDenis Read, 28, of Sarisbury Green,
OL,15,Fwas given a two-year and eight-month
OL,16,Fprison term; and Benjamin Jones, 23,
OL,17,Ffrom Eastleigh, was jailed for two
OL,18,Fyears and two months.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781432282
OL,3,CJudge highlights 'irony' of social
OL,4,Cmedia videos helping to catch
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FMariusz Szczyglo, 45 from Southampton,
OL,8,Fhad his case for the same charge
OL,9,Fadjourned to be sentenced on June 30.
OL,11,FSiobhan Linsley, prosecuting, said
OL,12,Fthat Jones was filmed picking up
OL,13,Fstones and throwing them at police on
OL,14,Fthree occasions, and kicking a bin
OL,15,Finto a parked car.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
