PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781432282
OL,3,CJudge highlights 'irony' of social
OL,4,Cmedia videos helping to catch
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FShe added: "He was first seen in
OL,8,FBelmont Road moving very quickly, he
OL,9,Fwas shouting at the riot officers
OL,10,Fwhile filming the disorder. He was
OL,11,Ffilming the small number of police
OL,12,Fbeing pursued by the baying crowd."
OL,14,FShe said Jones had one conviction for
OL,15,Fcriminal damage and common assault.
OL,26,@oD@LOUtD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
