PN,38607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781432282
OL,3,CJudge highlights 'irony' of social
OL,4,Cmedia videos helping to catch
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FStephen Tricker, representing Jones,
OL,8,Fsaid his client suffered from ADHD and
OL,9,Fautism, he "expresses sorrow and
OL,10,Fremorse" for his actions, and said it
OL,11,Fhad been an "impulsive decision" to
OL,12,Fjoin the protest.
OL,14,FMs Linsley said that Read was at the
OL,15,Ffront of the "aggressive" crowd and
OL,16,Fcould be seen kicking a bin and
OL,17,Fthrowing an item at close range at
OL,18,Fpolice, but missing, before throwing
OL,19,Fanother seven items including a glass
OL,20,Fbottle, small tree branches and a long
OL,21,Fpiece of plastic.
OL,26,@qD@LOUrD@HO]sD@MOUsD@`O]wD@NOUwD@YO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
