PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781432282
OL,3,CJudge highlights 'irony' of social
OL,4,Cmedia videos helping to catch
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FShe said that Read, a kitchen porter,
OL,8,Fhad four previous convictions for
OL,9,Fburglary, possession of cannabis and
OL,10,Fpossession of a bladed article.
OL,12,FThomas Acworth, defending, said:
OL,13,F"Denis Read knows what he did was
OL,14,Fwrong, Denis Read knows just how
OL,15,Fstupid he was but he is sorry for what
OL,16,Fhe did."
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
