CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781432282
OL,3,CJudge highlights 'irony' of social
OL,4,Cmedia videos helping to catch
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FMs Linsley said that Varney was filmed
OL,8,Fswearing at and threatening officers,
OL,9,Fand punching officers' riot shields
OL,10,Fthree times. She said he had a
OL,11,Fprevious conviction for battery.
OL,13,FKhalid Missouri, defending, said that
OL,14,FVarney had gone to Belmont Road to
OL,15,F"pay his respects" to Mr Nowak and he
OL,16,Fwas not affiliated with any of the
OL,17,Forganisers of the demonstration.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
