PN,38610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781432282
OL,3,CJudge highlights 'irony' of social
OL,4,Cmedia videos helping to catch
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FHe added that his client, who had been
OL,8,Ffilming the disorder with his phone,
OL,9,Fhad become angry after he was shoved,
OL,10,Fcausing him to drop his phone and
OL,11,Fbreaking it.
OL,13,FHe said: "He isn't targeting the
OL,14,Fpolice for what they did to Henry
OL,15,FNowak, his reaction to this is
OL,16,Ftriggered by his phone, something
OL,17,Fprecious to him, falling."
OL,26,@uD@JOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
