FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781432282
OL,3,CJudge highlights 'irony' of social
OL,4,Cmedia videos helping to catch
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FMr Missouri added that Varney had not
OL,8,Fbeen filming to share with others, as
OL,9,Fhe did not have any social media
OL,10,Fprofiles.
OL,12,FThe demonstration involving 1,000
OL,13,Fpeople started outside Southampton
OL,14,FCentral Police Station, before
OL,15,Fhundreds moved on to the Portswood
OL,16,Farea where Mr Nowak was killed, and
OL,17,Fwhere the violence started with, about
OL,18,F150 people remaining present, the
OL,19,Fcourt heard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781432282
OL,3,CJudge highlights 'irony' of social
OL,4,Cmedia videos helping to catch
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FAnger had erupted after police body-
OL,8,Fworn video was released showing Mr
OL,9,FNowak being placed in handcuffs
OL,10,Fmoments before he became unconscious
OL,11,Fand subsequently died.
OL,13,FVickrum Digwa, 23, who lived in a
OL,14,Fnearby road with his family, was
OL,15,Fjailed for life to serve a minimum of
OL,16,F21 years for his murder.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
