PN,38613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781432282
OL,3,CJudge highlights 'irony' of social
OL,4,Cmedia videos helping to catch
OL,5,Cprotesters
OL,7,FThe court hearings have been told that
OL,8,Fup to 13 police officers and a police
OL,9,Fdog were injured in the protest and a
OL,10,Fmember of the public suffered a broken
OL,11,Fjaw.
OL,13,FThe police operation involved 100
OL,14,Fofficers from nine different areas,
OL,15,Fwith a cost of #443,000, and a clean-
OL,16,Fup cost to the local council of
OL,17,F#7,000, the court heard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
